HEADWORD: Gallivant
<hw>Gal"li*vant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Gallant</er>.]</ety> <def>To play the beau; to wait upon the ladies;
also, to roam about for pleasure without any definite plan.</def>
<mark>[Slang]</mark> <rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
